OL,3,CMum of autistic boy fears for his
OL,4,Cfuture as council faces budget
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FStephanie Taylor told ITV News' Sam
OL,8,FBlackledge she's worried for her
OL,9,Fautistic son Hadyn's future.
OL,11,FThe mother of an autistic boy living
OL,12,Fin Plymouth says she is afraid for his
OL,13,Ffuture, as the city council faces
OL,14,Fmaking tough decisions on services for
OL,15,Fvulnerable people.
OL,17,FIt comes as families of children with
OL,18,Fspecial educational needs and
OL,19,Fdisabilities (SEND) call on
OL,20,Fcouncillors to prioritise them.
