OL,7,FThe local authority faces pressure on
OL,8,Fservices for vulnerable people and
OL,9,Fneeds to spend an extra #31million on
OL,10,Fadult social care, children's services
OL,11,Fand homelessness this year.
OL,13,FCouncil leader Tudor Evans has
OL,14,Finsisted that things are improving,
OL,15,Fbut said there will "never be enough
OL,16,Fmoney" to fund everything.
OL,18,F'I don't understand how they can
OL,19,Fignore our children'
