OL,7,F"They don't see SEND as a priority,
OL,8,Fand I can't understand why," she said.
OL,9,F"Of all the things that need funding
OL,10,Fand investing in, it's that.
OL,12,F"They are picking other things, like
OL,13,Fnew bus stops and regenerating the
OL,14,Fcity centre for the millionth time. I
OL,15,Fjust don't understand how they can
OL,16,Fignore our children like that."
OL,18,F'There is never going to be enough
OL,19,Fmoney'JThe council must find the
OL,20,Ffollowing funding over the coming year:
