OL,7,FCouncil leader Tudor Evans said that
OL,8,Fkeeping everyone happy while providing
OL,9,F300 services could be a tricky
OL,10,Fbalancing act.
OL,12,FHe added: "Those parents will know
OL,13,Fthat we have got an action plan for
OL,14,FSEND well under way. We have been
OL,15,Fputting more money into SEND than
OL,16,Fprevious years by quite some way. So
OL,17,Fwe are moving in the right direction.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
