OL,7,F"There's never going to be enough
OL,8,Fmoney and there is a waiting list for
OL,9,Fassessments. But we are working
OL,10,Fthrough it, we are going to improve it
OL,11,Fand we ask those parents to please
OL,12,Fbear with us, we will work through
OL,13,Fthis as quickly as we can."
OL,15,F'It requires people working together'
OL,17,FCllr Evans also promised more funding
OL,18,Ffor social care. However, care homes
OL,19,Flike Thornbury Villa in the Peverell
OL,20,Farea of Plymouth, have been feeling
OL,21,Fthe strain for many years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
