OL,3,CMum of autistic boy fears for his
OL,4,Cfuture as council faces budget
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,F"I think realistically you need to get
OL,8,Fentrepreneurs on board, you need to
OL,9,Fget business owners on board. We are
OL,10,Fproblem solvers.
OL,12,F"So I think closer working
OL,13,Frelationships with local authorities,
OL,14,Fcommissioners, government, see what's
OL,15,Fhappening on the ground so we can
OL,16,Factually make a whole change in the
OL,17,Fwhole system."
OL,19,FThe council's budget will be finalised
OL,20,Fin February 2025.
